snippet.title: I Tried Living Like The Rock For A Week!
snippet.description:
I Followed  @The Rock 's Daily Schedule For A Week!

What does the rocks daily schedule look like? In this video I follow what I would imagine the rocks daily routine and schedule would look like. I hope you enjoy!
